@startuml
title Diagrama de estados - Noticia / Artículo

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F8F8F8
  BorderColor #333333
}
skinparam ArrowColor #333333

[*] --> Draft : ArticleDraftCreated

Draft --> InReview : submitForReview / ArticleSubmittedForReview
Draft --> Archived : archive

InReview --> ChangesRequested : requestChanges / ArticleChangesRequested
InReview --> Approved : approve / ArticleApproved
InReview --> Archived : archive

ChangesRequested --> Draft : editAgain
ChangesRequested --> InReview : resubmit
ChangesRequested --> Archived : archive

Approved --> Scheduled : schedulePublication / ArticleScheduled
Approved --> Published : publishNow / ArticlePublished
Approved --> Draft : reopenDraft

Scheduled --> Published : publicationTimeReached / ArticlePublished
Scheduled --> Approved : cancelSchedule
Scheduled --> Unpublished : cancelPublication

Published --> Published : updateAfterPublication / ArticleUpdatedAfterPublication
Published --> Unpublished : unpublish / ArticleUnpublished
Published --> Archived : archivePublished

Unpublished --> Draft : editAsDraft
Unpublished --> Published : republish / ArticlePublished
Unpublished --> Archived : archive

Archived --> [*]

state Published {
  [*] --> AccessDecision
  AccessDecision --> PublicPublished : access_type = public
  AccessDecision --> PremiumPublished : access_type = premium

  PublicPublished : visible para visitantes, registrados y premium
  PublicPublished : publicidad discreta permitida
  PublicPublished : notificar registrados activos

  PremiumPublished : visible solo para premium activos
  PremiumPublished : cero publicidad
  PremiumPublished : notificar solo suscriptores activos
}

note right of Published
Al entrar en Published:
- insertar ArticlePublished en event_outbox
- workers actualizan feed, cache, búsqueda
- workers resuelven audiencia
- ads worker decide publicidad según access_type
end note

@enduml
